  <description><![CDATA[<p>A winter wonderland set in the remote Finnish fells, by beautiful Muonionjoki River separating Finland and Sweden. Located 200 kilometers above the Arctic Circle, you can fully embrace the peace and quiet of the real <a data-udi="umb://document/f83de191792e4f76a2b62b60cd414e3a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f83de191792e4f76a2b62b60cd414e3a}" title="Santa Breaks">Finnish Lapland</a>. The landscape is dominated by snow-covered forests, frozen lakes, and glistening hills, creating an authentic winter wonderland during the colder months. The remote location means that the skies are especially clear, giving you the chance to witness the magical Northern Lights. And it's the perfect place to meet Santa.</p>
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="tablet-button">
<tbody>
<tr style="height: 24px;">
<td><a data-udi="umb://document/c1571f262c9b49abb9ea19e974bc0fb3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c1571f262c9b49abb9ea19e974bc0fb3}" title="Muonio" class="c-btn"><strong>View all Muonio deals</strong></a></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<h2>Great value all-inclusive packages to Muonio</h2>
<p>A choice of 3 night stays departing Sundays and 4 night stays departing Wednesdays in December. We offer two all-inclusive packages either the traditional <a data-udi="umb://document/3a3eb0cda4234774a1795ec38e361e13" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3a3eb0cda4234774a1795ec38e361e13}" title="Harriniva Adventure Resort">Harriniva Wilderness Hotel</a>, or in cabins at lovely <a data-udi="umb://document/0bebfc4d25c141acaa0885b66699c486" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0bebfc4d25c141acaa0885b66699c486}" title="Jeris Lakeside Resort">Jeris Lakeside Resort</a>. The accommodation is furnished to a high standard, perfect for families looking for traditional Finnish accommodation, plus all of your excursions are included</p>
<h2>What's included in an Inghams holiday to Muonio</h2>
<ul>
<li><span>A private meeting with Santa and gift for children</span></li>
<li><span>Husky sled ride</span></li>
<li><span>Snowmobile Safari (adults drive whilst children ride in a sleigh)</span></li>
<li><span>Visit to reindeer farm and reindeer sleigh ride</span></li>
<li><span>Thermal suits and boots</span></li>
<li><span>More snow and fun activities</span></li>
<li><span>Flights from London Gatwick, Manchester and Bristol</span></li>
<li><span>Return transfers </span></li>
<li><span>Full board meals with complimentary soft drinks for children, coffee and tea in the hotel's main restaurants (excludes alcoholic drinks) at </span><a data-udi="umb://document/3a3eb0cda4234774a1795ec38e361e13" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3a3eb0cda4234774a1795ec38e361e13}" title="Harriniva Adventure Resort"><span>Harriniva</span> Adventure Resort</a> or <a data-udi="umb://document/0bebfc4d25c141acaa0885b66699c486" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0bebfc4d25c141acaa0885b66699c486}" title="Jeris Lakeside Resort" data-anchor="#">Jeris Lakeside Resort</a></li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<h2><span>Family Adventures in Lapland to see Santa</span></h2>
<p><span>Experience a world of enchantment  and feel the thrill as you slide down the slopes on a toboggan, race through the snowy fells on a snowmobile, embark on a magical husky safari through the magical untouched landscape or take a serene reindeer sleigh ride through the ancient Lappish farm.  You can also bake traditional Finnish gingerbread cookies, or craft your very own Christmas decorations to remember your enchanting trip to Lapland. The highlight of the day is experiencing the magic of meeting Santa in his hidden cabin, nestled among snow-covered trees and glistening icicles.  Each family will have a special meeting with Santa, where the children will receive a small gift. With enough Christmas magic, y</span><span>ou may even be lucky enough to </span>encounter the mystical Northern Lights, a magical display of dancing colours that paint the night sky with hues of emerald green, sapphire blue, and fiery red, it really is the greatest light show on earth. </p>
<p>Still have a question? See our <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/guest-services/frequently-asked-questions#santa-breaks" data-anchor="#santa-breaks">Santa Break FAQs</a>.</p>]]></description>
